{"tid":2048114,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"屌 陳偉豪選立法會","createTime":"2020-06-02T14:38:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-16T12:46:03.000Z","uid":59818,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8eb699916b5d39869afc0352c880e0de211ef22d","tid":2048114,"uid":59818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T14:38:20.000Z","msg":"有冇港足巴打分析下偉豪嘅打法啱唔啱議會戰線<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=393099\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D393099&d=9MYRmPDtC2YjWedq%2F%2FxxgVtf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=9471c1b1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D393099&h=a53e7a06\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=393099</a><br />\n體育、演藝、文化、出版界選民升幅同樣超過四成，亦大幅超出上屆選舉得票差距，不過，建制陣營對這界別的憂慮，一直不在於票數而是人選。馬逢國年屆65歲，要求他交棒的聲音大，而界別中亦有人不滿他忽視體育界的訴求，近日霍啟剛轉趨活躍，相信很大可能是交棒的對象。<br />\n<br />\n民主派方面，近日亦傳出一個出身體育界的名字&mdash;&mdash;前香港足球代表隊隊長陳偉豪。《政情》向陳偉豪查詢，他坦言基於朋友的提議，正考慮參選，希望可為運動員爭取合理權益，但還要視乎業界的討論，才決定是否去馬。"},{"pid":"a04f7555a4904d184a5695dc3aa2b68755a478ef","tid":2048114,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8eb699916b5d39869afc0352c880e0de211ef22d","tid":2048114,"uid":59818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T14:38:20.000Z","msg":"有冇港足巴打分析下偉豪嘅打法啱唔啱議會戰線<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=393099\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D393099&d=9MYRmPDtC2YjWedq%2F%2FxxgVtf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=9471c1b1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D393099&h=a53e7a06\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=393099</a><br />\n體育、演藝、文化、出版界選民升幅同樣超過四成，亦大幅超出上屆選舉得票差距，不過，建制陣營對這界別的憂慮，一直不在於票數而是人選。馬逢國年屆65歲，要求他交棒的聲音大，而界別中亦有人不滿他忽視體育界的訴求，近日霍啟剛轉趨活躍，相信很大可能是交棒的對象。<br />\n<br />\n民主派方面，近日亦傳出一個出身體育界的名字&mdash;&mdash;前香港足球代表隊隊長陳偉豪。《政情》向陳偉豪查詢，他坦言基於朋友的提議，正考慮參選，希望可為運動員爭取合理權益，但還要視乎業界的討論，才決定是否去馬。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T15:14:05.000Z","msg":"會唔會守到個龍門，唔好俾人搬黎搬去先？"},{"pid":"ba7413776bf41836a43ee210bfb81811033a73f1","tid":2048114,"uid":1241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T05:08:59.000Z","msg":"入去打柒啲獻世派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aba71c736e232868f796cd2860dbc8818dca9a28","tid":2048114,"uid":335780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T05:09:41.000Z","msg":"Good <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9e5fe000b6ae035eba4f1fe18e10a917db79c5e","tid":2048114,"uid":234998,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T05:48:17.000Z","msg":"我淨係知香港踢到最top都係最多3,4 萬月薪<br />\n做立會就起碼10萬月薪"},{"pid":"393ba78f32ef87554ab9a0db242b44bed7dae373","tid":2048114,"uid":70013,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a9e5fe000b6ae035eba4f1fe18e10a917db79c5e","tid":2048114,"uid":234998,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T05:48:17.000Z","msg":"我淨係知香港踢到最top都係最多3,4 萬月薪<br />\n做立會就起碼10萬月薪"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T05:49:44.000Z","msg":"佢全盛時有10萬但當時幾多都好啦<br />\n都退咗休"},{"pid":"a4d10d5fb9cde35089952c877f1b95173b345885","tid":2048114,"uid":5378,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a9e5fe000b6ae035eba4f1fe18e10a917db79c5e","tid":2048114,"uid":234998,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T05:48:17.000Z","msg":"我淨係知香港踢到最top都係最多3,4 萬月薪<br />\n做立會就起碼10萬月薪"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T05:52:38.000Z","msg":"咪撚on9啦 訓左幾多年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢跟羅神咁多年一定唔止呢個數"},{"pid":"3527d1071cc98b6e9a21f0ef15de7d667e0811dd","tid":2048114,"uid":252492,"li